        <updateDate>2006-11-28T17:35:40Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[Technology Investment Incentive Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) permit the expensing of certain technological equipment and computer software; and (2) include, for recovery purposes, as three-year property certain wireless telecommunications equipment, advanced services equipment, network or network system equipment, and research expenses for software development.]]></text>
      </summary>
